--- !u!114 &7040142369068303841
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 5371623121976236231}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5b72b968ab35b7747863b866328637d6, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuizManagerArun
  questions:
  - questionText: 1,Where was the hungry jackal?
    option1: In a theater.
    option2: In a circus.
    option3: 'In a forest. '
    option4: In a garden.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: cf19325191d4def48af17d1924912412, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 784a2e4b4388a444891330caeae34e3e, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 4
  - questionText: 2,What did the jackal hear?
    option1: A music concert.
    option2: Loud deafening sounds.
    option3: The sound of a waterfall
    option4: The sound of monkeys running.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 1
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e67ca549b418aa84ea0730345f4b9be4, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 35767121a7f27ba439c209ab3b50b075, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 4
  - questionText: 3,What did the jackal find when he went to investigate?
    option1: A huge sculpture.
    option2: A pack of wolves.
    option3: A deserted drum.
    option4: A restaurant.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0085c3fcae5aa8e45b7f7bce18da08bd, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 805bdd028d3eed448a85c0e4f671009b, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 7
  - questionText: 4,The jackal tore open the skin of the drum because
    option1: ...he thought something that made so much noise would be filled with
      food.
    option2: ...he thought it was a prey.
    option3: ...he thought tearing drum would be a fun activity.
    option4: he had nothing better to do
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 201d3fb844e9c7e41ac26af17188f074, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: a1f215c5cf7e00646b100f1b7184442f, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 0
  - questionText: 5,Why are we often scared of the unknown?
    option1: 'Because it could end up giving us homework. '
    option2: Because we fear Rakshashasas.
    option3: Because we fear of bad outcome
    option4: Because we have been told to be scared of the unknown
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: b9697da6431f2aa409a5019e700476bb, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: c296ea32d2ee0014290efb42a9c8e74f, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 5
  - questionText: 6,What is the worst thing to do when dealing with an unknown?
    option1: 'To be in a state of inaction. '
    option2: To investigate more about it.
    option3: To talk to friends about it.
    option4: To seek advice about
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: bbb2c39da8b169d4aa532018257e6622, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: fbd930edebac86148a29ea06c8031262, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 7
  - questionText: 7,What did Damanaka tell the king?
    option1: 'It''s time to eat dinner. '
    option2: "It's just a sound. But if you like, I can investigate it for you. \u2705 "
    option3: 'Where are we not acting in movies these days? '
    option4: 'I can teach you to make sounds like the bull '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 1
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: a593c966ce66a2f45bbe26af7c1bff8e, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 1d70d69a45ec55146b256853008118ae, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 0
  - questionText: '8. Why did Pingalaka think that Damanaka could have a grudge against
      him? '
    option1: 'For not playing games with him '
    option2: 'For being richer than him. '
    option3: 'For constantly eating ice cream without giving '
    option4: 'For not giving him a position in his ministry. '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7164efbaad720574f95a065180580124, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 94b45925822d9744c8e9874f6522606f, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 7
  - questionText: '9. What did Damanaka tell a scared Pingalaka? '
    option1: 'That he too was very scared of the creature. '
    option2: 'The creature was not present there any more. '
    option3: 'The relaxing and eating desserts would dissolve all fears '
    option4: 'That he would go and persuade the creature to come and meet him. '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4d8fcb449727c5e47bd88862ccb5ba01, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 47c10c9cff77de341968fc51075130bb, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: 10,What did the Sanjivika - the bull, tell Damanaka?
    option1: To buy him some Samosa.
    option2: To get him a job in the kingdom.
    option3: To work out his safety with the king.
    option4: To play football with him.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4ee1df4188c8dfd469daa21ed5dbe281, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 12ea025aaac20784785076d940a6ee66, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 7
  - questionText: 11,Damanaka described Sanjivaka as...anaka?
    option1: ...a death eater.
    option2: ...a deserted drum.
    option3: "...Shiva\u2019s vehicle"
    option4: ...a dinosaur
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: fb34670819f8ad84fb240a54b226a839, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: e82c1568bbec11941b7dc901eaad90ab, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
